tailed analysis of the dynamical\nentropy obtained via Lyapunov exponent which is rather an important quantity in\nthe study of deterministic systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jan 2020 18:30:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Jul 2020 05:58:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-22"}
